---
// src/components/About.astro — Premium About Section Responsive
const values = [
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg>`,
    text: "Segurança em Primeiro Lugar",
    color: "text-red-400"
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M13 2L3 14h9l-1 8 10-12h-9l1-8z"/></svg>`,
    text: "Inovação Contínua",
    color: "text-yellow-400"
  },
  {
    icon: `<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>`,
    text: "Transparência com o Cliente",
    color: "text-blue-400"
  }
];
---

<section id="sobre" class="relative py-16 sm:py-24 md:py-32">
  <div class="glow-orb-red absolute top-0 right-0 w-[300px] sm:w-[500px] h-[300px] sm:h-[500px] opacity-10"></div>

  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 sm:gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Image Side -->
      <div class="relative">
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/5">
          <img
            src="/assets/encryptedreuniao.png"
            alt="Equipe da Encrypted Software"
            class="w-full h-[250px] sm:h-[350px] md:h-[400px] object-cover"
          />
          <!-- Overlay gradient -->
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
        </div>

        <!-- Floating Stats Card -->
        <div class="absolute -bottom-4 sm:-bottom-6 right-2 sm:right-4 glass-card rounded-xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-3 sm:py-4 animate-float">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3">
            <div class="w-8 sm:w-10 h-8 sm:h-10 rounded-lg bg-red-500/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#ff1a1a" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-white">+50</p>
              <p class="text-[0.65rem] sm:text-xs text-gray-400">Projetos Entregues</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Text Side -->
      <div class="mt-6 lg:mt-0">
        <span class="section-badge mb-4 sm:mb-6 inline-flex">Quem Somos</span>

        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-4 sm:mb-6">
          Movidos por Desafios e<br/>
          <span class="text-gradient">Paixão por Tecnologia</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-gray-400 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed mb-3 sm:mb-4">
          A Encrypted Software nasceu da visão de que a segurança digital não é um luxo, mas uma necessidade fundamental. Somos arquitetos de soluções digitais robustas, obcecados por código limpo, performance e segurança.
        </p>

        <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-6 sm:mb-8">
          Nossa missão é transformar ideias complexas em softwares intuitivos e seguros, capacitando nossos clientes a inovar sem comprometer a proteção de seus dados.
        </p>

        <!-- Values -->
        <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4">
          {values.map(value => (
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 sm:gap-4 p-2.5 sm:p-3 rounded-xl border border-white/5 bg-white/[0.02] hover:bg-white/[0.04] transition-colors">
              <div class={`w-9 sm:w-10 h-9 sm:h-10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 bg-white/5 ${value.color}`} set:html={value.icon} />
              <span class="text-gray-200 font-medium text-sm sm:text-base">{value.text}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
